<p class="ayah 62-10" id="10" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُضِيَتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is concluded</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّلَوٲةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the prayer,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱنتَشِرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then disperse</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the land</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱبْتَغُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and seek</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَضْلِ ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Bounty of Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱذْكُرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and remember</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَثِيرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">much</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText t