<p class="ayah 62-11" id="11" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَأَوْاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they saw</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تِجَـٰرَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a transaction</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهْوًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a sport,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱنفَضُّوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they rushed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَتَرَكُوكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and left you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَآئِمًا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">standing.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`What</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِندَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) with</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</